headline: Nasdaq Sell-Off: 3 Top Dividend Stocks I Plan to Buy if the Nasdaq Keeps Falling
summary: The Nasdaq Composite has tumbled in recent weeks.  Here's why I'd love to buy more of these high-quality dividend stocks if the Nasdaq slump intensifies.  Broadcom's stock has lost about a quarter of its value from its price peak in the past year.
